    "bookShortLabel": "7下",
    "bookOrder": 211,
    "summary": "通过周健捐发做假发的故事，感受帮助他人带来的幸福。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s1",
      "text": "The wind was strong.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p1",
      "tr": "风很大。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "描述天气的基本句型。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/tyZ5Wg8Sfx62AFj4qi6kvi.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s2",
      "text": "Zhou Jian's hat blew off.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p1",
      "tr": "周健的帽子被吹掉了。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 副词",
      "d": "'blew off' 是动词短语，意为'吹掉'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Bwdf2GdhS7T4go4N8LxLdW.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s3",
      "text": "His long hair waved in the air.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p1",
      "tr": "他的长发在空中飘舞。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "形象地描写了头发随风飘动的样子。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ZVePLEi2BkyPY5KTs28Li2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s4",
      "text": "He heard a voice behind him: “Is that a boy or a girl?”",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p1",
      "tr": "他听到身后有声音：“那是男孩还是女孩？”",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "引语部分是一个选择疑问句。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/6JQNXdEWmuqfdZ8YVhjngY.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s5",
      "text": "He shook his head.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p1",
      "tr": "他摇了摇头。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "表示否认或无奈的动作。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/CTpgbcSrZzHLpkndcgLPyP.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s6",
      "text": "“Just one more month!” he said to himself.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p1",
      "tr": "“再坚持一个月！”他自言自语道。",
      "g": "直接引语 + 主语 + 谓语 + 对象",
      "d": "'said to himself' 意为'自言自语'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Gu69DsVTv3fhSrzk8MjacF.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s7",
      "text": "People often talked about his long hair behind his back.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p2",
      "tr": "人们经常在他背后议论他的长发。",
      "g": "主语 + 频度副词 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "'talk about' 意为'谈论'，'behind one's back' 意为'在某人背后'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UXpSqMXEdiP9BtUpwwAobY.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s8",
      "text": "Sometimes they laughed at him.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p2",
      "tr": "有时他们嘲笑他。",
      "g": "频度副词 + 主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "'laugh at' 意为'嘲笑'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/5neYhp2PLKAqEjmNtzeRi9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s9",
      "text": "But he never felt any shame.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p2",
      "tr": "但他从未感到羞耻。",
      "g": "连词 + 主语 + 频度副词 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "'felt' 是系动词，后接名词 'shame' 作表语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/eAZToeV4ofVxFu3MkbXrw6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s10",
      "text": "Zhou Jian kept his hair long for over two years.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p3",
      "tr": "周健留长发已经两年多了。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 宾补 + 时间状语",
      "d": "'keep + 宾语 + 形容词' 表示'保持某种状态'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/FPBKFjkCtesQeu3t4NTKBf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s11",
      "text": "Day after day, hope grew together with his hair.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p3",
      "tr": "日复一日，希望随着他的头发一起生长。",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主语 + 谓语 + 伴随状语",
      "d": "使用拟人手法，将'希望'具象化。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/gPeUKx9ZbekbZjE5WdS77h.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s12",
      "text": "Finally, the time came.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "终于，时间到了。",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主语 + 谓语",
      "d": "表示期待已久的时刻终于来临。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/h5oroGzvQYkeiUMetDEWQ7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s13",
      "text": "Zhou Jian walked into a barber's shop.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "周健走进了一家理发店。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "叙述动作发生的地点。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/WEmU4krjFmJ6PRiEf3xVVA.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s14",
      "text": "He took off his hat and his hair fell around his shoulders.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "他摘下帽子，头发散落在肩头。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 连词 + 主语 + 谓语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "并列句，描写了一连串的动作。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/3psuoBkpQKJz4z6CWUCzJ6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s15",
      "text": "The other customers were very surprised.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "其他顾客非常惊讶。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "描写周围人的反应。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/PtFZyXZqgePjpKoc3UcVgA.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s16",
      "text": "“Please cut it short and give me the hair,” he said.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "“请把它剪短，把头发给我，”他说。",
      "g": "祈使句 + 连词 + 祈使句",
      "d": "表达请求，'cut it short' 中 'short' 是宾语补足语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ovsMLCcnpYYvv38387J4Cg.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s17",
      "text": "The barber's scissors did their work.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "理发师的剪刀开始工作了。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "生动地描写剪发的过程。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/B4jmjEn7ZXdAqr3MjS9rRN.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s18",
      "text": "Zhou Jian carefully put the hair into a bag and walked to the post office.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p4",
      "tr": "周健小心翼翼地把头发放进袋子里，走向邮局。",
      "g": "主语 + 方式副词 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 地点状语 + 连词 + 谓语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "详细描述了一系列动作。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/VGyQ4u6uiM3vaiqgbvnABV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s19",
      "text": "A week later, he received a letter:",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p5",
      "tr": "一周后，他收到了一封信：",
      "g": "时间状语 + 主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "引出信件内容。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/y7mRAudx2TbkaAgDEKWwx7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s20",
      "text": "Dear Mr Zhou, Thank you for helping kids with cancer.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p5",
      "tr": "亲爱的周先生，感谢您帮助患癌症的孩子。",
      "g": "称呼 + 感谢句型",
      "d": "'Thank you for doing sth' 是标准感谢句型。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/PFBCZMNgEDtjM77exhZe6W.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s21",
      "text": "This is enough hair for three wigs!",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p5",
      "tr": "这些头发足够做三个假发！",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语 + 目的状语",
      "d": "说明捐赠头发的用途和价值。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/fEEK9qZ9vBFD7TruyjX6KV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s22",
      "text": "Thank you! The City Children's Hospital",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p5",
      "tr": "谢谢！市儿童医院",
      "g": "感谢语 + 落款",
      "d": "信件结尾。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/EQUWNNs5HyFzousWeQxBsX.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s23",
      "text": "Zhou Jian looked at the smart young man in the mirror.",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p6",
      "tr": "周健看着镜子里那个精神的年轻人。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 地点状语",
      "d": "'smart' 在这里意为'精神的、整洁的'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/sr66TuUCX7zT8z8ZRvrzK3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s24",
      "text": "He remembered the words of Plato: “Happiness springs from doing good and helping others.”",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p6",
      "tr": "他想起了柏拉图的话：“幸福源于行善和助人。”",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语（包含引语）",
      "d": "'springs from' 意为'源于'，引用名言点明主题。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/HoxnBzQrinPyX8dky9oe6N.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u4-article-s25",
      "text": "He smiled and said to himself, “It's time to grow happiness again.”",
      "paragraphId": "u4-article-p6",
      "tr": "他笑着对自己说：“是时候再次通过留发来‘种植’幸福了。”",
      "g": "主语 + 并列谓语 + 直接引语",
      "d": "首尾呼应，升华主题。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/k6tYCC3LCTqjy3nsC8oFyj.mp3"
    }
  ],
